text: Urjala is a municipality in Pirkanmaa, Finland. As of 30 September 2023, 4,581 people lived there. Neighbouring municipalities are Akaa, Forssa, Humppila, Hämeenlinna, Punkalaidun, Sastamala, Tammela and Vesilahti. == Other websites == * Municipality of Urjala – Official website Category:Municipalities of Pirkanmaa
title: Urjala
